<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/58510562-ayushi">Ayushi</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You can start with this book! It&apos;s a collection of stories and every story has a theme to it. Very engaging and enlightening! However, &apos;Kitchen&apos; is de<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You can start with this book! It's a collection of stories and every story has a theme to it. Very engaging and enlightening! However, 'Kitchen' is definitely the best of all her works. But you can go with this one for starters.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
