              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3859571016194590700">There’s something very sparse about these stories and I like that, there’s no over the top passion in the relationships. It’s even hard to work out what sex the narrator is and sometimes it felt like I had been reading it in the wrong voice, if that makes any sense. One of these stores was serialised on public transport, that must make commuting more interesting and I can’t imagine that happening here. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


