        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer8374066" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8373726436193846817">I read this book yesterday. I thought it would be a light read, since it was a six short stories compilation from Banana. Well, I was wrong. the book got me thinking a lot, and i think the stories fit the &apos;karma&apos; and &apos;spiritual&apos; themes Banana inspires very well.<br/><br/>My best bet is the last short story: A Strange River from Down the River. I find it relaxing, deep but also complicated. However, I still prefer her novels to her short stories.</span>
  <span id="freeText8373726436193846817" style="display:none">I read this book yesterday. I thought it would be a light read, since it was a six short stories compilation from Banana. Well, I was wrong. the book got me thinking a lot, and i think the stories fit the 'karma' and 'spiritual' themes Banana inspires very well.<br /><br />My best bet is the last short story: A Strange River from Down the River. I find it relaxing, deep but also complicated. However, I still prefer her novels to her short stories.</span>
